title: Pliskova, Suarez Navarro advance at Kremlin Cup
text: MOSCOW (AP) â€” Sixth-seeded Karolina Pliskova of the Czech Republic kept her hopes alive for a place at the season-ending WTA finals with a 6-4, 5-7, 7-6 (7) win over Romania's Alexandra Dulgheru in the first round of the Kremlin Cup on Tuesday.
